{"version":1,"entries":{"person_1381949_translations":{"at":1773688717274,"data":{"id":1381949,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Arswendy Beningswara Nasution (born on November 22, 1957) is an Indonesian actor, acting coach, and director of Mandailing descent. He studied Performing Arts at the Jakarta Institute of the Arts (IKJ) from 1978 to 1982.\n\nHis career began in theater, joining Teater Mandiri, led by Putu Wijaya. His film debut was Opera Jakarta in 1985. In addition to acting, Arswendy is also known as an acting coach for various films, such as Denias, Senandung Di Atas Awan and Merah Putih.\n\nSome of his most notable films include Satan’s Slaves (2017) as Ustad, Two Blue Stripes (2019) as Rudy, and Missing Home (2022) as Pak Domu. His role in Autobiography (2022) earned him the Best Actor award at the Marrakech International Film Festival.\n\nIn his personal life, Arswendy is the father of Eno Bening, a well-known Indonesian YouTuber.\n\nWith over three decades of experience, Arswendy Beningswara Nasution continues to make significant contributions to the Indonesian film and theater industry.","name":"Arswendy Bening Swara","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ID","iso_639_1":"id","name":"Bahasa indonesia","english_name":"Indonesian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Arswendy Bening Swara","primary":true}}]}},"person_2017395_translations":{"at":1773688717540,"data":{"id":2017395,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Jonathan Boynton-Lee","primary":true}}]}},"person_1032537_translations":{"at":1773688719365,"data":{"id":1032537,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Roberto Urbina","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"罗伯托·厄宾纳","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"רוברטו אורבינה","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"羅伯託·厄賓納","primary":false}}]}},"person_3447173_translations":{"at":1773688719451,"data":{"id":3447173,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Aj Bridel","primary":true}}]}},"person_1427726_translations":{"at":1773688720959,"data":{"id":1427726,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"杨雪，1980年10月16日出生于北京，毕业于北京电影学院表演系99级，中国内地女演员。\n\n2001年，出演都市爱情剧《非你不可》。2002年，主演TVB剧《血荐轩辕》。2003年，参演喜剧电影《一百万》。2004年，与佟大为主演电视剧《蝴蝶飞飞》饰演钟小印一角，被观众所熟知 。2005年，主演武侠剧《小鱼儿和花无缺》。2006年，主演爱情剧《我拿什么爱你》，同年在都市情感剧《明天我不是羔羊》中饰姜羽菲。\n\n2008年，主演平民情感剧《幸福里九号》。2009年，凭借战争剧《人间正道是沧桑》中林娥一角获得第16届上海电视节互联网大众票选最具潜力女演员奖。2010年，出演古装神话剧《活佛济公》，同年主演年代商战剧《烟雨斜阳》。2012年，主演抗战革命剧《红色黎明》。同年在古龙武侠剧《新圆月弯刀》中饰演青青。2013年，主演战争剧《信者无敌》。2014年，凭借出演的电影《西藏天空》获得第11届电影频道传媒大奖最佳新人女演员奖。","name":"杨雪","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yang Xue","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"楊雪","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Xue Yang","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"楊雪，1980 年 10 月 16 日出生於北京，畢業於北京電影學院表演系 99 級，中國內地女演員。\n\n2001 年，出演都市愛情劇《非你不可》。2002 年，主演 TVB 劇《血薦軒轅》。2003 年，參演喜劇電影《一百萬》。2004 年，與佟大為主演電視劇《蝴蝶飛飛》飾演鍾小印一角，被觀眾所熟知 。2005 年，主演武俠劇《小魚兒和花無缺》。2006 年，主演愛情劇《我拿什麼愛你》，同年在都市情感劇《明天我不是羔羊》中飾姜羽菲。\n\n2008 年，主演平民情感劇《幸福裏九號》。2009 年，憑藉戰爭劇《人間正道是滄桑》中林娥一角獲得第 16 屆上海電視節互聯網大眾票選最具潛力女演員獎。2010 年，出演古裝神話劇《活佛濟公》，同年主演年代商戰劇《煙雨斜陽》。2012 年，主演抗戰革命劇《紅色黎明》。同年在古龍武俠劇《新圓月彎刀》中飾演青青。2013 年，主演戰爭劇《信者無敵》。2014 年，憑藉出演的電影《西藏天空》獲得第 11 屆電影頻道傳媒大獎最佳新人女演員獎。","name":"楊雪","primary":false}}]}},"person_1671345_translations":{"at":1773688723214,"data":{"id":1671345,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Derek Chang","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"張軒睿","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"张轩睿（英语：Derek Chang，1992年12月17日－），台湾男艺人、演员及节目主持人，生于台北市，以电视剧《狼王子》中之演出获知名度。2018年，他以于《我的男孩》之演出，获第53届金钟奖最佳电视剧男主角提名。","name":"张轩睿","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Дерек Чан","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"張軒睿（英語：Derek Chang，1992 年 12 月 17 日－），台灣 男藝人、演員及節目主持人，生於台北市，以電視劇《狼王子》中之演出獲知名度。2018 年，他以於《我的男孩》之演出，獲第 53 屆金鐘獎最佳電視劇男主角提名。","name":"張軒睿","primary":false}}]}},"tv_95000_credits":{"at":1773688725750,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":237032,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Lo Chung-Him","original_name":"羅子溢","popularity":0.6508,"profile_path":"/dAc0eHm0CWBBu7L8KD84RrHAZyo.jpg","character":"","credit_id":"6443cf5f058224053d32ae91","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1143687,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Sammy Sum Chun-Hin","original_name":"沈震軒","popularity":0.5741,"profile_path":"/14JvAGteXhwqciX0uNAwdGaC20K.jpg","character":"","credit_id":"6443cf7b651fcf05069d2c61","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1772636,"known_for_department":"Acting"